QuestData.Title: Zealot's Dues
QuestData.Description:
Commander Domitille represents the very essence of the Nightborne's corruption. Abhorrent of power not their own, enamoured with their Grand Magistrix to the point of zealotry, and focused utterly on the destruction of the Moon Guard.
Take her helm to Lothrius as proof of her demise.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take Commander Domitille's Helm to Lothrius Mooncaller.
QuestData.RewardText: I was wondering why she had suddenly gone silent. It is a small comfort to my heart, but a great blow to the remaining forces of the Nightborne. Well done, $n.
